# CORS: comma-separated allowed origins (no spaces). Prefer whitelist over *.
# - Remote (LTE/зовнішній IP): додати http://ВАШ_IP та https://ВАШ_IP (якщо є SSL).
# - Nginx local: http://localhost,http://127.0.0.1
# - Dev (Vite 5173): http://localhost:5173,http://127.0.0.1:5173
# - LAN (опційно): http://192.168.x.x
# Example (office + public IP 95.47.196.98):
# CORS_ORIGINS=http://95.47.196.98,https://95.47.196.98,http://localhost,http://127.0.0.1,http://localhost:5173,http://127.0.0.1:5173
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost,http://127.0.0.1

